title: Reince Priebus Told White House Staff to Address Ivanka Trump and Jared Kushner as ‘Secretary’?
subtitle: An alleged White House staff e-mail was posted to an anonymous Twitter account.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: White House Chief of Staff Reince Priebus sent an e-mail to White House staff directing them to address Ivanka Trump and Jared Kushner as "secretary."
